page.title: 17Sample Plant Species,Rugby
page.content:
Children found the following plants on a walk round our D.Block:-
Buttercup,Ladies'Smock,Hedge Mustard, Wild Mustard,Shepherd's Purse,Pansy, White Campion,Red Campion,Mouse-ear chickweed,Common chickweed Corn Spurry Herb-Robert,Crane's-bill-round & cut- leaved,Medick,Red Clover,Common Vetch, Bramble,Hawthorn,Hogweed,Hedge Parsley Elder,Goosegrass,Daisy,Pineapple Weed, Scentless Mayweed,Wormwood,Ragwort, Groundsel,Hawkweed,Dandelion,Ash, Forget-me-not,Nightshade,Comfrey, Common Germander & Buxbaum's Speedwell Borage,Brooklime,Ground Ivy,Hedge Woundwort,Henbit,Red&White Dead-nettle Ribwort,Dock,Common Nettle,Bluebell, Hedge/Field Garlic,Ramsons,False Oat, Meadow Foxtail,Yorkshire Fog,Ryegrass, Barren Brome,Cock's-foot,Meadow-grass, Larch.
